These programs can be used to test the TIPC communication.

    |
    +- raw_tipc_transmitter
    |       Sends an ACTION and an EVENT each sencond with a running counter as payload.
    |
    +- raw_tipc_receiver
    |       Receives the ACTION and EVENT from the raw_tipc_transmitter.
    | 
    +- tipc_transmitter
    |       Sends an ACTION and an EVENT each second with a running counter as payload.
    |       Receives the ACK to an ACTION.
    | 
    \- tipc_receiver
            Receives the ACTION and EVENT from tipc_transmitter.
            Sends an ACK back on an ACTION.

